data.text: @brisbanetimes When I saw him live at QPAC here in Brisbane about 2 years ago, he had visibly slowed down physically, but was still so funny. I sadly realised it would be the final time I saw him live.
@brisbanetimes Better go to bed now (alone) before I get accused of something by hypocritic wowsers with political motives? Goodnight movers and shakers!
